bug.short_desc: Export to PPT doesn't display all German characters

long_desc.thetext:
I have a report that has the German characters:
örigen = örigen
When I view this report in the report viewer, the text appears correctly. However, when I export to PPT, the text appears as:
örigen =rigen
Plus, there's an extra ':' character at the end of the output.
See attached output.jpg.
